Hi I'm a CAMS student who began his live journal on may 11, 2002 at 5:44 pm
......

***********************

MUAhahaha Hi all, I'm this mofo who is 26 yrs old, recently rediscovered livejournal because I have this brilliant idea. Actually i have many. After so many yrs of college, things like this tend to happen. I have finders that cannot control the keyboard. this shit is literally being ripped from the neurons wrapping on the outer surface of my white matter within my skull.

Basically i think Ferris Beullers day off is over. This motherfucker who is an 80s icon must return. When this guy made this movie, he was 24 yrs old. ONLY 2 yrs younger than me and he is memorable for his babyface character as IMDB recalls. I just saw the fucken clips and I see how this fatass has let go. He can totally redo his persona. He did inspector gadget. We should all write to him and the studios, because I have the script in possession. I have what will redo this 80s phenommenon. And we shall call it Ferris Beuler's Day of Reality.........


Everyone loved this film because this guy never got caught. Well now that life sucks, this economy is in shit and he is wayyy older. The guy is a family man. He is literally, the family guy. Mixing persona's and what this guy is known for. The comedy will be there however we will require less dramatic shit, adding reality to the mix. If anyone recently saw the changeup, I'm sure you get my drift. Family requires tons of energy and tolerance. It's fucken reality. We need to bring the 80s back, because this icon merits a circle of life sequel.
